title: Jaguar Journals
overview: Jaguar Journals follows expert wildlife biologist and TV personality, Lizzie Daly as she joins groundbreaking monitoring projects. Using the latest tagging-technology, Lizzie uncovers exciting new insights into animal behavior and reveals how to protect wildlife. Jaguar Journals combines emotional and dramatic storytelling with the scientific purpose of Lizzie's mission across the series.Each episode returns to the leading cast of jaguar characters in gripping storylines that keep the audience coming back for more.
